### Note on SCP-173

The photograph of the sculpture depicted in SCP-173 ("Untitled 2004" by
Izumi Kato) is **not** under a free license and may not be used for
commercial purposes. See https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/licensing-guide
for details.
